<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
 <head>
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <!-- Optional theme -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
    <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Titillium+Web' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link href="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.1.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", :media => "all" %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

    <!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.9.1.js"></script>
    
    <!-- Latest compiled and minified JavaScript -->
    <script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jasny-bootstrap/3.0.1-p7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="//code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.3/jquery-ui.js"></script>
  </head>

	<body>
		<nav class="navbar navbar-fixed-top navbar-default" role="navigation">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-ex1-collapse">
            <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </button>
          <%= link_to "Home", root_path, :class => "navbar-brand" %>
        </div>

        <!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse navbar-ex1-collapse">
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
            <li class="<%= 'active' if current_page?(about_path) %>"><%= link_to "ABOUT", about_path %></li>
            <li class="<%= 'active' if current_page?(new_contact_path) %>"><%= link_to "CONTACT", new_contact_path %></li>
            <% if user_signed_in? %>        
		      		<li><%= link_to 'NEW POST', new_post_path %></li>
              <li class="<%= 'active' if current_page?(notifications_path) %>">
                <%= link_to notifications_path do %>
                  <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
                  <% if current_user.mailbox.receipts.where(is_read: false).any? %>
                    <span class="unread-count"><%= current_user.mailbox.receipts.where(is_read: false).count %></span>
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>
              </li>
              <li>
                <%= link_to current_user do %>
                  <i class="fa fa-user"></i>&nbsp;<%= current_user.name %>
                <% end %>
              </li>
		      		<li class="dropdown">
				        <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown"><i class="fa fa-gear"></i></a>
				        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                  <li><%= link_to "FINANCES", finances_path %></li>
				          <li><%= link_to "ACCOUNT SETTINGS", edit_user_registration_path %></li>
			            <li><%= link_to "LOGOUT", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %></li>
			        	</ul>
	      			</li>
      			<% else %>
  	        	<li><%= link_to "<i class='fa fa-user'></i>&nbsp;SIGN IN".html_safe, "#myModal", :data => {:toggle=>"modal"} %></li>  		
      			<% end %>
          </ul>
        </div><!-- /.navbar-collapse -->
      </div><!-- /.container -->
    </nav> 

    <%= render "layouts/signin" %><!-- signin modal -->

    <div class="theme-background">
      <% if notice %>
        <div class="alert alert-success" style="margin-bottom: -5px;">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">×</button>
          <%= notice %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if alert %>
        <div class="alert alert-warning">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">×</button>
          <%= alert %>
        </div>
      <% end %> 
  		<%= yield %>
    </div>

    <div id="fwfooter">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1" id="footer-content">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 footer-col">
              <h4>About Company</h4>
              <hr>
              <p>Aliquam dui lobortis vestibulum amet sit per sodales proin cursus suscipit sapien netus fermentum eleifend phasellus nam torquent mollis sociis conubia venenatis vivamus commodo enim cras eu sit integer massa</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-1 list-unstyled footer-col">
              <li><h4>Company</h4></li>
              <hr class="hr-offset">
              <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Blog</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Press</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Jobs</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Investors</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="col-md-2 list-unstyled footer-col">
              <li><h4>User</h4></li>
              <hr class="hr-offset">
              <li><a href="#">Starting a fund</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Accepting a fund</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Advertising</a></li>
            </ul> 
            <ul class="col-md-3 list-unstyled footer-col">
              <li><h4>Get Help</h4></li>
              <hr class="hr-offset">
              <li><a href="#">FAQ</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Customer Support</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Return Policy</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Terms Of Use</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Privacy Statement</a></li>
            </ul>
          </dvi>
        </div>      
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <script>
      $('.user-info-hover').popover({trigger: 'hover'});
    </script>
		<!-- Latest compiled and minified JavaScript -->
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
	</body>
</html>